text: Otto Hoogesteyn (11 January 1903 - 7 June 1966) was a Dutch swimmer. He competed in the men's 4 × 200 metre freestyle relay event at the 1924 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1903 births Category:1966 deaths Category:Dutch male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of the Netherlands Category:Swimmers at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Wiesbaden
